Description: Broadcom MegaRAID StorCLI storage management tool
 StorCLI is the command-line management tool for Broadcom MegaRAID RAID
 controllers. It provides complete control over RAID configuration and
 monitoring, including creating and managing virtual drives, checking drive
 health, monitoring controller status, and updating firmware.
 .
 StorCLI is the successor to MegaCLI and supports all Broadcom/LSI MegaRAID
 SAS/SATA/NVMe controllers.
 .
 This package contains the storcli64 binary installed as /usr/sbin/storcli.
 .
